\begin_layout Section*
Budget Justification
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Hardware compute resources have already been procured, and so hardware expenditu
res of less than $10K are expected.
 The nature of this research does not seem to require the use of, or interaction
 with LLMs, GPT, or any of the deep–learning neural net systems; thus a
 budget of zero for LLMs is anticipated.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Some of the contemplated theoretical models might run much faster if ported
 to GPU's.
 Perhaps the theory may indicate that the descriptive, declarative systems
 resemble TensorFlow.
 If so, then a contingency must be set aside for rental of cloud–compute
 resources.
 However, the need for this, and the nature of this need is entirely unclear.
 There's a shadow of a hint at the edges; how it comes into play remains
 unknown.
 The current work is a low–level exploration of theory, and has not reached
 the stage of being compute–hungry.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The budget is primarily that of the salary for the lead researcher.
